entries.femaleVariant: Nothin' quite like blastin' at a target. Right away, you just feel... Powerful, you know?
Hm, yeah. I guess... I dunno. Not really feeling it.
I mean it's fine, don't get me wrong. But I'm not getting chills or anything.
Yeah, know the feeling. You need something real, not these dummies.
Look, I know a guy who organizes runs on NID. Homeless hunting.
Put you in touch. Guarantee you'll get some chills then.
Hmmm, I... What about the cops?
Oh, please. They got bigger problems than a few forgotten meatbags.
